#21802
Chamber of the Wheel~
A massive mural covers the floor of this room, depicting the
cycle of life and death, seasons and elements. Near the top
of the circle are depictions of paradise and nearer the bottom
are depictions of suffering and torment. You note with some
interest that demonic looking oni are shown in nearly all of the
scenes, some carrying people on their backs up to paradise,
others dragging people away to suffer hellish torment. The
Great Buddha is shown near the top and nearer the bottom
is shown a great armor clad figure, a stern look on his face.
All about the room are closed portals, each marked with
symbols of the elements.
~
